// Shows:
//   - Module-level log_* convenience functions
//   - Adjusting the default logger's minimum level
//   - Named Logger instances with per-module prefixes
//   - ERROR / FATAL routing to stderr
//   - Timing work with the Timer class

include "github.com/jeffscottbrown/jerry-logging"

fn main() {
    log_info("hello");
}
